    "author_association": "NONE",
    "body": "### Problem\n\nTo be precise: the key is executed once both when pressed and when released\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nnvim -u NONE file.txt\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nPressing a key once executes the key once\n\n### Nvim version (nvim -v)\n\nNVIM v0.12.0 \n\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\n\nno，VIM - Vi IMproved 9.1 (2024 Jan 02, compiled Apr 01 2025 20:12:31)\n\n### Operating system/version\n\nubuntu24.04 LTS\n\n### Terminal name/version\n\nkitty 0.32.2 created by Kovid Goyal\n\n### $TERM environment variable\n\nxterm-256color\n\n### Installation\n\nSource code installation tag: v0.12.1",
